List of Functionalities

    1. Auto initialization if the attribute data-formValidate is present
    2. Allows customization
        •	Change the attribute data-formValidation
        •	Change the default trigger event
        •	Enable/disable focusing the first field with error
        •	Enable/disable hiding error on change of value
        •	Auto scroll to error field
        •	Allows used defined validations
        •   Allows customized error and success messages on form header
        •   Customizable CSS for error and success msgs

    3. User defined validation for alphabets included in app.js to demonstrate user defined validation functionality.
    4. User can specify if field needs to be mandatory using "isRequired". if it is set to false, then the field won't be validated on blur.
    

List of attributes : 
    • email
    • password 
    • number 
    • telephone 
    • alphaNumeric 
    • alphaNumericWithSpecialChar 
    • zipcode 
    • address 
    • url 
    • mmddyyyy (date format supports '.','/','-' seperators)
    • ddmmyyyy (date format supports '.','/','-' seperators)
    • yyyymmdd (date format supports '.','/','-' seperators)

    